WEBVTT

00:05.386 --> 00:09.320
<i>♪</i>

00:09.322 --> 00:12.122
Whatever.

00:12.125 --> 00:13.792
Oh, you're watching
"Making a Supervillian?"

00:13.794 --> 00:14.758
I finished the whole thing last night.

00:14.760 --> 00:16.394
Well, do not tell me how it ends,

00:16.396 --> 00:17.862
but I think he's innocent.

00:17.864 --> 00:20.098
Seriously? His name is Dr. Psycho.

00:20.100 --> 00:23.468
Yeah, but his original
name was Psychowitz.

00:23.470 --> 00:25.470
They forced him to
change it at Ellis Island.

00:25.472 --> 00:28.840
The real villain is the
criminal justice system.

00:28.842 --> 00:29.841
Go on, girl.

00:29.843 --> 00:30.889
Idiots. Okay.

00:30.892 --> 00:32.944
He tied Wonder Woman to a rocket ship.

00:32.946 --> 00:35.246
Oh, the D.A. said he
tied her to a rocket ship,

00:35.248 --> 00:37.282
but if that's the case,
where's the rope, Teddy?

00:37.284 --> 00:39.651
- Where's the rope then?
- Find it. Prove it.

00:39.653 --> 00:41.486
Oh, I've seen this program.

00:41.488 --> 00:43.454
I can't believe they found him innocent.

00:43.456 --> 00:45.590
Dorothy!

00:45.592 --> 00:47.659
You bitch.

00:50.664 --> 00:57.602
<i>♪</i>

